♪ Linger-linger-lingering love ♪

415
00:23:55,901 --> 00:23:58,905
♪ Just won't let me be ♪

416
00:23:58,937 --> 00:24:02,350
♪ Well, my baby, she's gone,
but my love lingers on ♪

417
00:24:02,374 --> 00:24:04,911
♪ And on and on and on ♪

418
00:24:05,911 --> 00:24:09,552
♪ Mountains tall
and desert wide ♪

419
00:24:09,581 --> 00:24:12,790
♪ Where can I run, baby,
where can I hide? ♪

420
00:24:12,818 --> 00:24:16,391
♪ Love for my baby
won't behave ♪

421
00:24:16,421 --> 00:24:19,698
♪ I guess it's gonna follow me
to my grave ♪

422
00:24:19,724 --> 00:24:22,967
♪ Linger-linger-lingering love ♪

423
00:24:22,994 --> 00:24:25,998
♪ Just won't let me be ♪

424
00:24:26,031 --> 00:24:28,011
♪ Well, my baby,
