896
00:54:25,595 --> 00:54:29,133
I mean, you know I am
pretty darn good at what I do,

897
00:54:29,165 --> 00:54:31,577
like finding out things.

898
00:54:31,601 --> 00:54:35,174
I mean, that's why folks
call on Maurice Doucette,

899
