out to Mexico.

906
00:54:55,625 --> 00:54:59,095
Instead there's poor old Dale.

907
00:54:59,129 --> 00:55:01,370
He's deader than
Chief Billy Bowlegs

908
00:55:01,398 --> 00:55:03,400
out of the Third Seminole War,

909
