937
00:56:18,541 --> 00:56:20,384
Well, that's just dandy.

938
00:56:20,410 --> 00:56:22,788
What, did he go and rob that bank
right under your nose?

939
00:56:22,812 --> 00:56:25,088
No. Not quite, no.

940
00:56:25,115 --> 00:56:28,562
No, I didn't add it all up
until I saw the paper this morning.

941
00:56:28,585 --> 00:56:31,395
Then it all made
a whole lot of sense.

942
00:56:31,421 --> 00:56:33,594
- What did?
- Hell, when you spend all your time

943
00:56:33,623 --> 00:56:35,625
following a man around
day in and day out,

944
00:56:35,658 --> 00:56:38,104
