997
00:59:06,609 --> 00:59:09,556
I swear, Lorna,
I didn't so much as touch the man.

998
00:59:09,579 --> 00:59:12,219
Oh, you did a lot more
than touch him.

999
00:59:12,248 --> 00:59:15,161
