like bunnies.

1001
00:59:17,020 --> 00:59:18,795
Go on, tell her
what you done.

1002
00:59:18,821 --> 00:59:20,926
She ain't lying.

1003
00:59:20,957 --> 00:59:22,231
No.

1004
